## Rules

### TEST-001: Coverage Gate
severity: ERROR
scope: all production code in src/
rule: Unit test coverage MUST meet or exceed the configured minimum. Pull requests that reduce coverage below the threshold MUST NOT be merged.
threshold: min_coverage_pct=80, max_test_file_lines=300
example_correct: |
  # All branches covered, edge cases tested
  def test_error_path(): ...
  def test_happy_path(): ...
example_incorrect: |
  # Only happy-path tests — coverage at 40%

### TEST-002: Test Independence
severity: ERROR
scope: all test files
rule: Tests MUST be independent and MUST NOT share mutable state between test cases. Tests that depend on execution order are prohibited. Each test MUST set up its own fixtures.
threshold: max_test_file_lines=300
example_correct: |
  def test_process(tmp_path):
      # tmp_path is fresh per test
      ...
example_incorrect: |
  _shared_state = {}  # mutable module-level — prohibited
